CatDescriptText: Cutline of related images published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 7, 1956, pg. 3 reads: "Cute 'Honeybunnies' Paraded... and captured the hears of everyone at the fashion show at A. Leo Weil School. Wearing perky spring outfits with sparkling smiles on their faces, some came out in pairs, as a single, or in one instance, as a trio..."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of boys and girls modeling Easter fashions in A. Leo Weil School, Hill District
